import { Box, Card, CardContent, CardMedia, Typography } from '@mui/material'
import React from 'react'
import Slider from "react-slick";
import building from '../../Assets/Images/buliding.jpeg'

const TrandingProjects = () => {


  const settings = {
    className: "center",
    centerMode: true,
    infinite: true,
    centerPadding: "60px",
    slidesToShow: 3,
    speed: 500,
    rows: 2,
    slidesPerRow: 3,
    dots: true
  };

  return (
    <Box pt={3} p={3}  mt={5}>
      <Typography variant='h5' component='div' fontWeight={600}>
        Trending Projects
         </Typography>
        <Typography variant='subtitle2' color='#747474'>
            Most sought-after projects in Thane
        </Typography>
        
        <Box mt={2}>
        <Slider {...settings}>
            <Card sx={{display:'flex'}}>
              <Box sx={{display:'flex' , flexDirection: 'column'}}>
                <CardMedia component='img' 
                image={building}
                />
                  
              </Box>
              <Box sx={{display:'flex'}}>
              <CardContent sx={{flexGrow:'1', flex: '1 0 auto' }}>
                <Typography>
                  Title
                </Typography>
                
              </CardContent>
              </Box>
             

            </Card>
         </Slider>
        </Box>
       


    </Box>
  )
}

export default TrandingProjects
